mming and group tours at the location in coordination with the Outreach and Programming Team and the Branch Manager. Responsible for addressing the conduct of members and visitors that violates Idea Exchange’s code of conduct. Acts as Person in Charge when assigned.Opens and closes building when requested and assists with monitoring building security when scheduled. Cover Member Services and Information Services duties as required.Under the direction of the Manager, Queen’s Square Adult Services, execute new initiatives and perform other duties as required.What
